title: [MTV] Real World Sydney
description:
The Real World: Sydney is the nineteenth season of MTV&#039;s popular reality television series The Real World, which focuses on seven diverse strangers living together for several months in a different city each season, as cameras follow their lives and interpersonal relationships. Every season of The Real World, beginning with its fifth season, has included the assignment of a season-long group job or task to the housemates. This season, the cast is assigned to work for Contiki Tours, a vacation travel package planning company, creating a Sydney tour package.
